{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017giYaQFrfGsxApCKAVoizV","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n     2→\n     3→### Session 10 — state corruption fix (2026-03-27T14:15Z)\n     4→\n     5→- Stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 were at `review` in sprint-state.json despite being committed as `done` with proof documents in git (commits 09ae9a0, 4d6af09, f597711, 5b7fa94).\n     6→- Epic 16 was at `backlog` in sprint-status.yaml despite commit cb82adb marking it complete.\n     7→- Root cause: ralph state reconciliation overwrites committed state. This is a recurring issue (also seen in session 9).\n     8→- Fixed manually by updating sprint-state.json and sprint-status.yaml to match git truth.\n     9→- No stories executed this session — all work was already done.\n    10→\n    11→## Token Report\n    12→- Total tool calls: ~12\n    13→- By tool: Read: 3, Bash: 5, Edit: 1, Glob: 1, Write: 1\n    14→- Files read: 4 unique, 5 total reads\n    15→- Redundant operations: None\n    16→\n    17→### State corruption fix (2026-03-27T13:48Z)\n    18→\n    19→Stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7 were at `review` in sprint-state.json despite committed as done with proof documents. Fixed by restoring `done` status. Same root cause as previous session — ralph state reconciliation overwriting committed state.\n    20→\n    21→### 16-8-update-all-tests — create-story (2026-03-27T13:49Z)\n    22→\n    23→- Ambiguity in epic definition: Task 8 in tech-spec is terse (\"Update all tests\") with no specific ACs. Derived ACs from tech-spec testing strategy.\n    24→- Used legacy tag names (`cli-verifiable`) per instruction — `LEGACY_TIER_MAP` maps them to `test-provable` at parse time.\n    25→- Risk: Story may require zero code changes if previous stories already added all tests.\n    26→\n    27→## Token Report\n    28→- Total tool calls: 17\n    29→- By tool: Read: 7, Grep: 7, Glob: 3, Write: 1\n    30→- Files read: 9 unique, 10 total reads\n    31→- Redundant operations: None\n    32→\n    33→### 16-8-update-all-tests — dev (2026-03-27T13:56Z)\n    34→\n    35→- Pre-existing BATS failures: 6 BATS integration tests fail (ralph loop tests, unrelated to verification tier rework).\n    36→- Zero code changes needed — audit confirmed complete coverage from stories 16-1 through 16-7.\n    37→\n    38→## Token Report\n    39→- Total tool calls: 16\n    40→- By tool: Bash: 6, Read: 9, Write: 1, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n    41→- Files read: 9 unique, 9 total reads\n    42→- Redundant operations: None\n    43→\n    44→### 16-8-update-all-tests — code-review (2026-03-27T14:00Z)\n    45→\n    46→- LOW-1: `classifyTier` barrel re-export not tested through index.ts\n    47→- LOW-2: Line number references in Dev Agent Record will drift\n    48→- LOW-3: No explicit test for runtime > test priority in classifyTier\n    49→\n    50→## Token Report\n    51→- Total tool calls: 15\n    52→- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 9, Edit: 2, Grep: 3, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n    53→- Files read: 12 unique, 12 total reads\n    54→- Redundant operations: None\n    55→\n    56→### 16-8-update-all-tests — verify (2026-03-27T14:05Z)\n    57→\n    58→ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs). Test-provable tier — no Docker needed. Build, 4015 tests, coverage 96.86%.\n    59→\n    60→## Token Report\n    61→- Total tool calls: 17\n    62→- By tool: Bash: 9, Read: 3, Grep: 8, Write: 2\n    63→- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n    64→- Redundant operations: Proof written twice (format fix). Separate vitest runs for pass count vs coverage.\n    65→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01XQb88j2XyoAEyWba8pEnv2","session_id":"9a32080c-76ef-409a-9a0e-138b5be12a95","uuid":"15842baf-8bcc-4fdc-a478-0f4de2b56609","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:17:14.056Z"}
